  "3026830": {
    "name": "Alex The Ball",
    "steam_appid": 3026830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于物理</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >球真的在滚动。即使你没有按下按钮，它可能仍在运动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能量系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将决定小球跳多高，但需要在它跳起之前做出决定。时机至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/fca880a02a608f45f3e6651e6af9654c.poster.avif?t=1749459715\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/fca880a02a608f45f3e6651e6af9654c.webm?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/fca880a02a608f45f3e6651e6af9654c.mp4?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲刺/慢动作模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞄准时，时间会变慢，你要利用能量来推动球。利用这一点，你就能在最后关头获救。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/538d73a67a57ffac3d7645fed2c8eb4b.poster.avif?t=1749459715\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/538d73a67a57ffac3d7645fed2c8eb4b.webm?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/538d73a67a57ffac3d7645fed2c8eb4b.mp4?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能量提升</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你收集能量加成时，你的最大能量就会增加，其他一些参数也会随着能量的增加而提高。你将变得更加强大。尽量不要错过这些东西，因为将来你可能需要跳过更大的缺口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/def8b5a0ce5d86b71f1e6dc78181a90a.poster.avif?t=1749459715\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/def8b5a0ce5d86b71f1e6dc78181a90a.webm?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/def8b5a0ce5d86b71f1e6dc78181a90a.mp4?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漂浮物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些物体会漂浮在空中。当你落在上面时，它们可能不会停留在原地。小心为妙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/e41bf41c6991ac396ab857465053720a.poster.avif?t=1749459715\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/e41bf41c6991ac396ab857465053720a.webm?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/e41bf41c6991ac396ab857465053720a.mp4?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >周围有一些小触手。乍一看，它们似乎没什么作用，但它们不会轻易离开你，如果它们在你周围待的时间够长，你就会死亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/fca880a02a608f45f3e6651e6af9654c.poster.avif?t=1749459715\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/fca880a02a608f45f3e6651e6af9654c.webm?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/fca880a02a608f45f3e6651e6af9654c.mp4?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些益智元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些门是锁着的，你需要找到按钮来打开它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/7f589e298abdd5cbc63f4f087bd156f1.poster.avif?t=1749459715\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/7f589e298abdd5cbc63f4f087bd156f1.webm?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026830/extras/7f589e298abdd5cbc63f4f087bd156f1.mp4?t=1749459715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >检查点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中设有检查点系统，但显然你必须先到达检查点。祝你好运</p>",
